<eesti>Maasekret&auml;ri ametikohal t&ouml;&ouml;tamise eritingimus </eesti>
<inglise>Special condition for employment in position of county secretary </inglise>
<eesti>Seaduse j&otilde;ustumisel maasekret&auml;rina t&ouml;&ouml;taval isikul on &otilde;igus j&auml;tkata oma ametikohal, kui ta on asunud &otilde;ppima k&otilde;rgemat juriidilist haridust andvas &otilde;ppeasutuses. </eesti>
<inglise>A person employed in the position of county secretary upon the entry into force of this Act has the right to continue in his or her office if the person undertakes studies in an educational institution which offers higher education in law. </inglise>
<eesti>See &otilde;igus l&otilde;peb, kui ta katkestab &otilde;pingud k&otilde;rgemat juriidilist haridust omandamata. </eesti>
<inglise>This right shall terminate if the person stops his or her studies without acquiring higher education in law. </inglise>
